title: Fly into Porto Princessa and land on the updated airport  #msfs2020
description:
Puerto Princesa International Airport (IATA: PPS, ICAO: RPVP) serves the Puerto Princesa area in the province of Palawan, Philippines. The Civil Aviation Authority of the Philippines classifies it as an international airport. A significant update in MSFS not only enhances the airport but also the surrounding areas, making it an excellent upgrade for frequent flyers in this region.
